INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('5', '1', '2013-07-23 06:32:14', '2013-07-23 06:32:14', '&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://mauitropicalmassage.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/AdrianThailand.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-363\" src=\"http://mauitropicalmassage.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/AdrianThailand-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"Maui Yoga &amp; Wellness Retreat instructor\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<b>Adrians bio:</b>   <b>Adrian </b>has been studying massage &amp; yoga passionately since 2004.  He chose one of the best massage schools in the world,  Maui School of Therapuetic Massage, graduating in September 2010 where he honed his skills in <b>Lomi Lomi, Swedish, Sports Massage, NMT, Deep Tissue</b>, and more.  Upon request he can also introduce sound therapy with Tibetan Healing bowls, and a high end <b>Tactile</b> <b>Sound Healing</b> table.  He spent 9 months in India studying at various yoga schools, ashrams &amp; meditations centers including a 2 month yoga intensive at <a title=\"Agama Yoga School \" href=\"http://www.AgamaYoga.com\" target=\"_blank\">Agama Yoga</a> in Rishikesh, India followed by a 500 hours/3 month teachers training at their mother school in Koh Phangan, Thailand.  He prefers to teach meditation at the moment but can do private yoga classes upon request.\r\n\r\n<em>He continues his education constantly learning to help people lighten up &amp; ENLIGHTEN UP with Yoga, Massage, Meditation &amp; Sound Healing.</em>\r\n\r\n<em>Experience</em> ::  *650 hour/ 12 month Massage Therapy program - September 2010 in Maui, Hawaii.\r\n\r\n*500 hours/3month Hatha Yoga teachers training at Agama Yoga in Koh Phangan, Thailand in 2009.\r\n\r\n*5 extra months of yoga intensive trainings at Agama Yoga school in Rishikesh, India Sept/Oct 2007 &amp; Thailand 2009.\r\n\r\n<b>*</b>Yoga University – June &amp; August 2013, Maui-Hawaii\r\n\r\n<b>*</b>Access Bars – energy healing training July 2013, Maui-Hawaii.\r\n\r\n*Kailash School of Ayurveda Massage – October 2006.  3 week course in Dharamsala, India.\r\n\r\n*Sunshine School of Thai Massage – June 2009, 10 day course in Chang Mai, Thailand.\r\n\r\n*Lomi Lomi 2 day intensive workshop – July 2005, Vancouver BC.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://mauitropicalmassage.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Tirzah-bio-headshot.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-362\" src=\"http://mauitropicalmassage.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Tirzah-bio-headshot-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"Maui Yoga teacher &amp; Massage LMT\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><strong>Tirzah\'s bio:  </strong>Tirzah is a cheerful, certified yoga instructor, professional massage therapist, sacred sexuality advocate and hula hoop enthusiast. She has been happily practicing yoga for over a decade. She deeply resonates with the Tantric path as it has captivated her with its extraordinary teachings for many years. Tirzah has studied extensively for five months at Agama Tantra Yoga University in Thailand. She is wholeheartedly passionate about spiritual evolution, as it continues to shift her consciousness in profound ways. <span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">                          </span>Tirzah is a citizen of the world and has received the richest education through travel. She genuinely adores culture shock, barefeet, dreaming, acro yoga flying, coconuts, laughter, writing, celebrations, expansion, waterslides and being upside down. And she LOVES love. Tirzah is highly optimistic about living fully and focuses her time and energy on experiences rather than material things. She is currently working on quieting her crazy ego, following her heart\'s footsteps, and recognizing challenges as grand opportunities for growth.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Neenel\'s bio:  </strong>Neenel is a body centered life coach who is dedicated to personal growth and transformation. She holds a Bachelors degree in Community Studies from the University of California, Santa Cruz.   She is a 400hr certified yoga teacher who received her foundational training at Kailash Tribal Yoga School in Dharmasala, India and continued her training in the US, studying Kundalini Yoga, as taught by Yogi Bhajan.  Currently, she is working towards her Counseling Masters degree.  Her professional background also includes working locally in community mental health, co-facilitating clinical counseling groups, and leading forty day transformational retreats.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-35 aligncenter\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Lola6-199x300.jpg\" alt=\"Lola6\" width=\"199\" height=\"300\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Lola’s bio:</strong>  Lola  has an extensive and diversified background in yoga, movement, and music. Her esoteric, yoga and dance studies range in subject matter from Hatha Yoga, Naam Yoga, Pilates, Belly Dance, Jazz Dance, Gyrotonic, West African, Harmonyum, astro-physics with the Resonance Project, Merkabah Meditation, Theta Healing, music production and Classical as well as Jazz Vocal Studies.\r\n\r\nIn addition, she likes to explore ancient and modern healing techniques while inquiring within her own heart and higher spirit for guidance to a more sustainable and healthier way of living, such as permaculture, Theta healing meditation, essential oils for natural health and living in community. Most recently, she\'s dancing for Iona 360 Dance Company  Maui chapter  (contemporary, experimental dance ), she\'s excited to start dancing professionally again.\r\n\r\nWhen she’s not at her studio teaching, taking a workshop, singing or making music, Lola enjoys chanting to the ocean waves, hiking to waterfalls, being outside amongst the trees, exploring raw super-food recipes, and sun gazing.\r\n\r\n<b> </b><em>experience ::</em>\r\n\r\n<b>*</b>Yoga University – June &amp; August 2013, Maui-Hawaii\r\n\r\n<b>*</b>Access Bars – energy healing training July 2013, Maui-Hawaii.\r\n\r\n*Yoga Works- 200 hour Hatha Yoga 2011, Mill Valley, CA.\r\n\r\n* Naam Yoga– 200 hour yoga specializing in mantra, meditation, kundalini, kabalah, numerology and mudras. Santa Monica, CA\r\n\r\n*Harmonyum- energy work accessing sunlight energy to clear karma. Santa Monica, CA\r\n\r\n*Acro Yoga- Wanderlust Festival, 2010, 2011, 2012\r\n\r\n*Pilates- Integrative Teacher Training, Im=X Pilates, Joseph Pilates Method and Advanced Exercises, Many workshops on post-rehabilitative exercises\r\n\r\n*Gyrotonic and Gyrokinesis Certified Miami Beach including Jump Board Certification\r\n\r\n*Living Light Raw Foods Educator Certification 2010, Mendocino, CA\r\n\r\n*Zumba Certification 2010, Santa Cruz, CA\r\n\r\n*Theta Healing Plant, Animal and Soul Mate Workshop 2013, Idaho Falls, ID\r\n\r\n* Essential Oils workshops at DoTerra University\r\n\r\n<b> </b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b> </b>', 'About', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'about', '', '', '2015-09-14 07:31:42', '2015-09-14 17:31:42', '', '0', '/?page_id=5', '0', 'page', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('6', '1', '2013-07-23 06:32:36', '2013-07-23 06:32:36', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\">MAUI WELLNESS TOURS &amp; RETREATS</p>\r\nPRIVATE YOGA CLASSES  @ Ananda Sanctuary (or mobile)\r\none-on-one OR small private group lessons which give you the benefit of\r\n*choosing what day/time you want to practice\r\n*customize your yoga lesson to fit your level, whether complete beginner or not\r\n*address any injuries, questions about preventing injuries &amp; get more one-on-one attention\r\n*customize your yoga lesson to do exactly what you want to do in class: asanas, pranayma, meditation, etc..\r\n\r\nWe are registered with Yoga Alliance &amp; insured with Namasta. In 2009 Adrian completed a 500 hour 3 month teachers training with Agama Yoga, a Hatha Yoga which practices the full 8 limbs of Yoga, generally very slow paced, holding poses for 2-3 minutes with deep stretching. If desired we can get into Yoga theory such as Chakras &amp; Energy channels awakened with each asana, &amp; do breathing exercises of Pranayama which are very profound at bringing deep peace &amp; harmony within the Being. Adrian has traveled 9 months in India studying at various yoga schools, completing a 2 month yoga intensive in Rishikesh at Trika Yoga school, a 3 week yoga course in Dharamsala &amp; visiting many ashrams. His style taught is Hatha Yoga, aka \'original yoga\'.\r\n\r\nChristina teaches Kundalini Yoga (Naam yoga style), Partner Yoga, Pilates, Gyrokinesis/Gyrotonics &amp; more.\r\nPlease refer to her website for details:\r\nwww.ChristinaAmar.com\r\n\r\nClass can be set to music or you can listen to the sounds of the tropical birds.\r\nPerfect for beginners to learn the basic postures and proper alignment. Also classes for intermediate yogis\r\nlooking to try out different styles.\r\n\r\nClasses at Ananda Sanctuary, located one mile from Twin Falls in Huelo (outer Haiku)\r\n* COMBINE YOUR TWIN FALLS HIKE WITH a private Yoga/Pilates/Gyro class, Massage, etc..\r\n\r\nOR\r\nat your condo, home, apartment, or pick your favourite beach. . ..we come to you!\r\n*$10-20 extra charge depending on location\r\n\r\nprices:\r\n$60 1-3 people\r\n$80 4-6 people\r\n$100 7-10 people\r\n\r\n*possible private lessons could include lectures on explanations of asanas such as:\r\npadahastasana, talasana, sahaja agnisara dhauti, bhujangasana, paschimottanasana, vajrasana, surya namaskar, cakrasana, gomukhasana, garudasana, sarvangasana, ardha sirsasana, uddiyana bhanda, dhanurasana, pavana muktasana, salabhasana, svastikasana, , halasana, ardha matsyendhrasana, final relaxation\r\n\r\n*lectures giving detailed explanations of powerful yogic techniques &amp; theory such as ::\r\ncleansing purifications of sanka praksalana &amp; vamana dhauti\r\nsleeping aid of Nidra Yoga\r\npeaceful trancendental inducing AUM meditation (mantra initiation)', 'Yoga', '', 'private', 'open', 'open', '', 'yoga', '', '', '2017-04-05 15:58:17', '2017-04-06 01:58:17', '', '0', '/?page_id=6', '0', 'page', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('8', '1', '2013-07-23 06:33:25', '2013-07-23 16:33:25', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Maui Tropical Massage :: \"Enlighten Up with Massage!\"</strong></p>\r\n<strong>Massage offered on site at our boutique spa, or...we send one of our therapists to you!  Yes, Maui Tropical Massage is mobile as well &amp; service all sides of the island North, South, East &amp; West!  </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>2 LMT\'s at your service for couples &amp; simultaneous family massage!  </strong>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Maui_Wellness_Retreat_Massage2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-169\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Maui_Wellness_Retreat_Massage2-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"Maui_Wellness_Retreat_Massage2\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" /></a>\r\n\r\n1) <strong>60 minutes</strong> – got only 1-2 areas that need work?  This will give me 20-3o minutes to focus on those areas and/or a full body massage to briefly cover other areas.<strong>  $80</strong>\r\n\r\n2) <strong>90 minutes</strong> – this will give your body more time for the attention needed to thoroughly address problem areas &amp; bring you into a state of deep relaxation &amp; harmony. <strong>$110</strong>\r\n\r\n3) <strong>120 minutes</strong> – Ahhhhh…how often does one really treat themselves to this kind of treat?  Not enough!  Bring the mind/body/soul into a state of deep relaxation.  Experience a full body professional massage with no hurries!  <strong>$140 </strong>\r\n\r\n4) <strong>30 minutes</strong> – In a hurry?  No worries…this quick fix will get you back in shape in a jiffy!  <strong>$40</strong>\r\n\r\nCall now to book an appointment.\r\n\r\n808.463.5856\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nAdditional Charges:\r\n\r\n•  $20 extra fee if we drive to your location for mobile massage fee.\r\n•  Hotel or Condo Valet Parking up to $10.00+Tip, unless there is free parking available.\r\n•  Booking Massages on the West Side Maui requires two or more Massages that day (tell your friends/neighbors &amp; get booked simultaneously!)\r\n•  Same Day Cancellation fee of $20.00\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Sound Healing Table </strong>\r\n\r\nExperience the deep cathartic relaxation of a high end “Tactile Sound Table”, essentially, a massage table with speakers on it!\r\n\r\nScience has proved that sound/vibrations have a profound effect in the harmonization of cells &amp; our well-being!\r\n\r\nThe cells of our bodies ‘sing’ to each other, a form of intracellular communication, and do it most effectively in the range 100 to 1000 Hertz with the Tactile Sound Table!\r\n\r\nYou can choose to get a treatment combined with massage therapy, Or use the Sound Healing Table on its own with special recordings made for the table such as:\r\n\r\n*7 Chakra tune-up     *Spine/Vertabrae tune-up    *Binaural Beats journey\r\n\r\n*Didgeridoo Dreamtime      *And many more customized playlists\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nPrices:  $60 hour for Sound Healing Table\r\n\r\n$140 hour with Massage + Sound Healing Table\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n“Oxytocin is released when music is played, like an orgasm.  Music is transcendental, empowering &amp; defuses tension in the body. Simply put, MUSIC IS MEDICINE!”', 'Massage', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'massage', '', '', '2016-10-23 22:05:23', '2016-10-24 08:05:23', '', '0', '/?page_id=8', '0', 'page', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('298', '1', '2014-07-04 16:15:38', '2014-07-05 02:15:38', '<h2 id=\"424509125121511502\" class=\"element wsite-content-title editable-text\">Access Consciousness BarsA 1-Day Mini Retreat &amp; Training\n\nFriday August  22nd in Huelo 9:30-5:30pm\n\nRegister at <a style=\"color: #ad190f;\" href=\"http://www.accessconsciousness.com/class_details.asp?cid=46153\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.accessconsciousness.com/class_details.asp?cid=46153</a>\n<span style=\"color: #125b8c;\">\n</span>\n<span style=\"color: #125b8c;\">Have you done a lot of personal growth work, but still feel stuck in some key areas?</span>Would you like to experience more ease in your work, body, money flows, &amp; relationships?\n\nWhat if you had tools to change anything that is not working for you with speed, ease, and joy?\n\nCome laugh, play, relax, &amp; expand your reality with tools that will serve you for the rest of your life!\n\nAccess Consciousness® is a fun and practical system of tools, processes and questions that dynamically clear limitations quickly and effectively in the areas of:\n\n<strong>body,  relationships,  work,  money,  parenting,  spirit</strong>\n\nand anywhere you would like to clear blocks and have more ease &amp; joy! Access Consciousness acknowledges that we change the planet by living in greater happiness, and that when we really *get*our magnificence,  we begin to naturally contribute to the world in magical ways!\n\n\nkids free!!\n\nTry it for $10 suggested donation on Thursdays   email Kathy at <a style=\"color: #ad190f;\">smartrelief@gmail. com</a>\n\nor call <a style=\"color: #ad190f;\" href=\"tel:808-268-%208708\" target=\"_blank\">808-268- 8708</a>\n\nTaught by Kathy Williams, facilitating energy work and transformation with clients for 14 years.\n\nFor more about Kathy, click <a style=\"color: #ad190f;\" href=\"http://www.bars.accessconsciousness.com/fac_detail.asp?mid=1461\" target=\"_blank\">Here</a>\n\nWhen you expand beyond the confines of your mind (the known, the past), you can begin to create your life from true possibility, expansion, and flow!\n\nRead on for what class participants have to say:\n\n<strong>\"If you feel even the slightest bit curious,\n</strong>I encourage you to attend Kathy\'s Bars class, <strong>\nit <em>will</em> change your life in a way you can not even begin to imagine.\nIt has already significantly changed mine and\nall done in ease, flow, and joy in just one day.\"   Marise, Kihei, Maui</strong>\n\n\"I love Kathy\'s enthusiasm, devotion and embodiment of the Access tools. Her Bars class is fun and lively!  I found the clearing statements invaluable. \"     Amrita Grace\n\n\nRegister &amp; more info     <a style=\"color: #ad190f;\" href=\"http://www.accessconsciousness.com/class_details.asp?cid=46153\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.accessconsciousness.com/class_details.asp?cid=46153</a>\nor email <a style=\"color: #ad190f;\">smartrelief@gmail.com</a>\n\n<a style=\"color: #ad190f;\" href=\"http://www.iotransformation.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Classes ~ Healing Sessions ~ Access Bars Trainings ~ Yoga Therapy</a>\n\n<a style=\"color: #ad190f;\" href=\"http://www.iotransformation.com/\" target=\"_blank\">www.iotransformation.com</a></h2>', '1 Day Retreat & Training ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '223-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-07-04 16:15:38', '2014-07-05 02:15:38', '', '223', '/223-autosave-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
