INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('44', '1', '2013-07-25 05:03:40', '2013-07-25 05:03:40', '<strong>Lola’s bio:</strong>  Lola Amar has an extensive and diversified background in yoga, movement, and music. Her esoteric, yoga and dance studies range in subject matter from Hatha Yoga, Naam Yoga, Pilates, Belly Dance, Hula, Gyrotonic, West African, Harmonyum, astro-physics with the Resonance Project, Merkabah Meditation, Theta Healing, music production and Classical as well as Jazz Vocal Studies.\r\n\r\nIn addition, she likes to explore ancient and modern healing techniques while inquiring within her own heart and higher spirit for guidance to a more sustainable and healthier way of living, such as permaculture, Theta healing meditation, essential oils for natural health and living in community.\r\n\r\nWhen she’s not at her studio teaching, taking a workshop, singing or making music, Lola enjoys chanting to the ocean waves, hiking to waterfalls, being outside amongst the trees, exploring raw super-food recipes, and sun gazing.\r\n\r\n<b> </b>experience ::\r\n\r\n<b>*</b>Yoga University – June &amp; August 2013, Maui-Hawaii\r\n\r\n<b>*</b>Access Bars – energy healing training July 2013, Maui-Hawaii.\r\n\r\n*Yoga Works- 200 hour hatha yoga 2011, Mill Valley, CA.\r\n\r\n* Naam Yoga– 200 hour yoga specializing in mantra, meditation, kundalini, kabalah, numerology and mudras. Santa Monica, CA\r\n\r\n*Harmonyum- energy work accessing sunlight energy to clear karma. Santa Monica, CA\r\n\r\n*Acro Yoga- Wanderlust Festival, 2010, 2011, 2012\r\n\r\n*Pilates- Integrative Teacher Training, Im=X Pilates, Joseph Pilates Method and Advanced Exercises, Many workshops on post-rehabilitative exercises\r\n\r\n*Gyrotonic and Gyrokinesis Certified Miami Beach including Jump Board Certification\r\n\r\n*Living Light Raw Foods Educator Certification 2010, Mendocino, CA\r\n\r\n*Zumba Certification 2010, Santa Cruz, CA\r\n\r\n*Theta Healing Plant, Animal and Soul Mate Workshop 2013, Idaho Falls, ID\r\n\r\n* Essential Oils workshops at DoTerra University\r\n\r\n<b> </b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b> </b>\r\n\r\n<b>Adrians bio:</b>   <b>Adrian </b>has been studying massage &amp; yoga since 2004.  He chose one of the best massage schools in the world,  Maui School of Therapuetic Massage, graduating in September 2010 from a 650 hour program where he honed his skills in <b>Lomi Lomi, Swedish, Sports Massage, NMT, Deep Tissue</b>, and more.  Upon request he can also introduce sound therapy with Tibetan Healing bowls, and a high end <b>Tactile</b> <b>Sound Healing</b> table.  He spent 9 months in India studying at various yoga schools, ashrams &amp; meditations centers including a 2 month yoga intensive at Agama Yoga in Rishikesh, India followed by a 500 hours/3 month teachers training at their mother school in Koh Phangan, Thailand.\r\n\r\nHe continues his education constantly learning to help people lighten up &amp; ENLIGHTEN UP with Yoga, Massage, Meditation &amp; Sound Healing.\r\n\r\nexperience ::\r\n\r\n<b>*</b>Yoga University – June &amp; August 2013, Maui-Hawaii\r\n\r\n<b>*</b>Access Bars – energy healing training July 2013, Maui-Hawaii.\r\n\r\n*Kailash School of Ayurveda Massage – October 2006.  3 week course in Dharamsala, India.\r\n\r\n*Sunshine School of Thai Massage – June 2009, 10 day course in Chang Mai, Thailand.\r\n\r\n*Lomi Lomi 2 day intensive workshop – July 2005, Vancouver BC.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'About Us ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '5-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-07-25 05:03:40', '2013-07-25 05:03:40', '', '5', '/2013/07/25/5-revision-2/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('45', '1', '2013-07-25 07:46:52', '2013-07-25 07:46:52', '<strong>Massage offered on site @ Ananda Sanctuary or mobile at your place.</strong>\n\n<strong>2 LMT\'s at your service for couples &amp; simultaneous family massage!  </strong>\n\n1) <strong>60 minutes</strong> – got only 1-2 areas that need work?  This will give me 20-3o minutes to focus on those areas and/or a full body massage to briefly cover other areas.<strong>  $80</strong>\n\n2) <strong>90 minutes</strong> – this will give your body more time for the attention needed to thoroughly address problem areas &amp; bring you into a state of deep relaxation &amp; harmony. <strong>$110</strong>\n\n3) <strong>120 minutes</strong> – Ahhhhh…how often does one really treat themselves to this kind of treat?  Not enough!  Bring the mind/body/soul into a state of deep relaxation.  Experience a full body professional massage with no hurries!  <strong>$140 </strong>\n\n4) <strong>30 minutes</strong> – In a hurry?  No worries…this quick fix will get you back in shape in a jiffy!  <strong>$40</strong>\n\nCall now to book an appointment.\n\n808.463.5856\n\n&nbsp;\n\nAdditional Charges:\n\n•  $20 extra fee if I drive to your location (gas &amp; time).\n•  Hotel or Condo Valet Parking up to $10.00+Tip, unless there is free parking available.\n•  Booking Massages on the West Side Maui requires two or more Massages that day (tell your friends/neighbors &amp; get booked simultaneously!)\n•  Same Day Cancellation fee of $20.00\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>Sound Healing Table </strong>\n\nExperience the deep cathartic relaxation of a high end “Tactile Sound Table”, essentially, a massage table with speakers on it!\n\nScience has proved that sound/vibrations have a profound effect in the harmonization of cells &amp; our well-being!\n\nThe cells of our bodies ‘sing’ to each other, a form of intracellular communication, and do it most effectively in the range 100 to 1000 Hertz with the Tactile Sound Table!\n\nYou can choose to get a treatment combined with massage therapy, Or use the Sound Healing Table on its own with special recordings made for the table such as:\n\n*7 Chakra tune-up     *Spine/Vertabrae tune-up    *Binaural Beats journey\n\n*Didgeridoo Dreamtime      *And many more customized playlists\n\n&nbsp;\n\nPrices:  $60 hour for Sound Healing Table\n\n$140 hour with Massage + Sound Healing Table\n\n&nbsp;\n\n“Oxytocin is released when music is played, like an orgasm.  Music is transcendental, empowering &amp; defuses tension in the body. Simply put, MUSIC IS MEDICINE!”', 'Massage ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '8-autosave-v1', '', '', '2013-07-25 07:46:52', '2013-07-25 07:46:52', '', '8', '/2013/07/25/8-autosave/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
