INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('48', '1', '2013-07-25 08:07:35', '2013-07-25 08:07:35', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\">MAUI WELLNESS TOURS &amp; RETREATS</p>\nPRIVATE YOGA CLASSES  @ Ananda Sanctuary (or mobile)\none-on-one OR small private group lessons which give you the benefit of\n*choosing what day/time you want to practice\n*customize your yoga lesson to fit your level, whether complete beginner or not\n*address any injuries, questions about preventing injuries &amp; get more one-on-one attention\n*customize your yoga lesson to do exactly what you want to do in class: asanas, pranayma, meditation, etc..\n\nWe are registered with Yoga Alliance &amp; insured with Namasta. In 2009 Adrian completed a 500 hour 3 month teachers training with Agama Yoga, a Hatha Yoga which practices the full 8 limbs of Yoga, generally very slow paced, holding poses for 2-3 minutes with deep stretching. If desired we can get into Yoga theory such as Chakras &amp; Energy channels awakened with each asana, &amp; do breathing exercises of Pranayama which are very profound at bringing deep peace &amp; harmony within the Being. Adrian has traveled 9 months in India studying at various yoga schools, completing a 2 month yoga intensive in Rishikesh at Trika Yoga school, a 3 week yoga course in Dharamsala &amp; visiting many ashrams. His style taught is Hatha Yoga, aka \'original yoga\'\n\nClass can be set to music or you can listen to the sounds of the tropical birds.\nPerfect for beginners to learn the basic postures and proper alignment. Also classes for intermediate yogis\nlooking to try out different styles.\n\nI am currently teaching Hatha yoga at Ananda Sanctuary in Haiku, Maui, a beautiful oasis\nhome studio where me &amp; my partner Christina Lola Amar own/operate a sacred space for Yoga, Dance, Movement &amp; Workshops.\n\nChristina teaches Kundalini Yoga (Naam yoga style), Partner Yoga, Pilates, Gyrokinesis/Gyrotonics &amp; more.\nPlease refer to her website for details:\nwww.ChristinaAmar.com\n\n\nClasses at Ananda Sanctuary, located one mile from Twin Falls in Huelo (outer Haiku)\n* COMBINE YOUR TWIN FALLS HIKE WITH a private Yoga/Pilates/Gyro class, Massage, etc..\n\nOR\nat your condo, home, apartment, or pick your favourite beach. . ..we come to you!\n*$10-20 extra charge depending on location\n\nprices:\n$60 1-3 people\n$80 4-6 people\n$100 7-10 people\n\n\n*possible private lessons could include lectures on explanations of asanas such as:\npadahastasana, talasana, sahaja agnisara dhauti, bhujangasana, paschimottanasana, vajrasana, surya namaskar, cakrasana, gomukhasana, garudasana, sarvangasana, ardha sirsasana, uddiyana bhanda, dhanurasana, pavana muktasana, salabhasana, svastikasana, , halasana, ardha matsyendhrasana, final relaxation\n\n*lectures giving detailed explanations of powerful yogic techniques &amp; theory such as ::\ncleansing purifications of sanka praksalana &amp; vamana dhauti\nsleeping aid of Nidra Yoga\npeaceful trancendental inducing AUM meditation (mantra initiation)', 'Yoga', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '6-autosave-v1', '', '', '2013-07-25 08:07:35', '2013-07-25 08:07:35', '', '6', '/2013/07/25/6-autosave/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
