e=\"Pranayama\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pranayama\">pranayama</a>, and <a title=\"Meditations\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meditations\">meditations</a> which target the whole body system (<a title=\"Nervous system\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nervous_system\">nervous system</a>, <a title=\"Glands\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Glands\">glands</a>, mental faculties, <a title=\"Chakras\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chakras\">chakras</a>) to develop awareness, consciousness and spiritual strength.\" —<a title=\"Yogi Bhajan\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Yogi_Bhajan\">Yogi Bhajan</a></blockquote>', 'Kundalini Yoga', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '96-autosave-v1', '', '', '2013-09-23 02:48:53', '2013-09-23 02:48:53', '', '96', '/2013/09/23/96-autosave-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
