INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('229', '1', '2013-10-17 10:29:45', '2013-10-17 20:29:45', '<strong>1) Magic Movie Night :: Ananda Sanctuary monthly event.  Next date TBA  @ Ananda Sanctuary </strong>\r\npotluck beginning at 6pm, followed by a few interesting magical movies &amp; ecstatic dance party. FREE.\r\n\r\n<strong>2)  FREE MEDITATION circle.  Next date TBA</strong>.    6-7pm, followed by potluck.  This new moon is particularly potent for healing past karma, genetic ancestral karma &amp; we will tune into that healing energy.\r\n\r\nStyle of mediation will vary each gathering.  Exploring various techniques using silent mantras, meditations from Osho\'s books, Ram Dass meditation book, or just plain sitting in silence with group.\r\n\r\nMeditation is a blessed way for human beings to connect with Spirit.  I find it truly calming, well after the first few minutes of mind chattering.  I am a total advocate for this type of “Medicine” because for one it works.  The connection of body, mind and spirit is that of healing.\r\n\r\nThe great masters before have expressed over and over again the benefits of meditation.  It consist of the following:\r\n\r\n100 Benefits of Meditation ::\r\nhttp://www.ineedmotivation.com/blog/2008/05/100-benefits-of-meditation/\r\n\r\nAnd this site has some cute explanations of what Meditation does ::\r\nhttp://www.emmaseppala.com/10-science-based-reasons-start-meditating-today-infographic/#.U2qoa61dVhg\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #222222;\">3)  </span><span style=\"color: #222222;\">Maui Healing Arts Skills trade monthly circle - next date TBA</span></strong>\r\n<span style=\"color: #222222;\"> </span>\r\n<span style=\"color: #222222;\">Location: Maui Wellness Center, aka Ananda Sanctuary in Huelo just makai from Twin Falls (directions on www.AnandaYogaSanctuary.com). Come share your skills, learn some new techniques, help each other expand &amp; grow &amp; get out of the same ole routines. Bring your massage tables &amp; lets empower each other!   </span><span style=\"color: #222222;\">Can be for massage, energy work &amp; other healing modalities.</span>\r\n<span style=\"color: #222222;\">*Cant speak for you all, but I\'ve wanted to take so many continuing ed massage workshops, that just didnt seem affordable or in my priorities the past few years. Receiving massage if you are alert, can be a way to learn, but i\'m one of those people that need to practice, practice, practice.</span>\r\n<span style=\"color: #222222;\">Soo.....this is what we will all do: Share, practice, integrate, receive, then give. </span>\r\n<span style=\"color: #222222;\">\r\n</span>Facebook Event page:   TBA\r\n\r\nJoin new Facebook Group \"Maui Healing Artists\" &amp; share with healers you know:\r\n<a style=\"color: #ad190f;\" title=\"\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/226437894212827/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/226437894212827/</a><span style=\"color: #222222;\">\r\n</span>', 'Monthly Events', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hatha-yoga-ttc', '', '', '2015-08-03 16:37:38', '2015-08-04 02:37:38', '', '0', '/?page_id=229', '0', 'page', '', '0');
