qoa61dVhg\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #222222;\">3)  </span><span style=\"color: #222222;\">Maui Healing Arts Skills trade monthly circle - next date TBA</span></strong>\r\n<span style=\"color: #222222;\"> </span>\r\n<span style=\"color: #222222;\">Location: Maui Wellness Center, aka Ananda Sanctuary in Huelo just makai from Twin Falls (directions on www.AnandaYogaSanctuary.com). Come share your skills, learn some new techniques, help each other expand &amp; grow &amp; get out of the same ole routines. Bring your massage tables &amp; lets empower each other!   </span><span style=\"color: #222222;\">Can be for massage, energy work &amp; other healing modalities.</span>\r\n<span style=\"color: #222222;\">*Cant speak for you all, but I\'ve wanted to take so many continuing ed massage workshops, that just didnt seem affordable or in my priorities the past few years. Receiving massage if you are alert, can be a way to learn, but i\'m one of those people that need to practice, practice, practice.</span>\r\n<span style=\"color: #222222;\">Soo.....this is what we will all do: Share, practice, integrate, receive, then give. </span>\r\n<span style=\"color: #222222;\">\r\n</span>Facebook Event page:   TBA\r\n\r\nJoin new Facebook Group \"Maui Healing Artists\" &amp; share with healers you know:\r\n<a style=\"color: #ad190f;\" title=\"\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/226437894212827/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/226437894212827/</a><span style=\"color: #222222;\">\r\n</span>', 'Monthly Events', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '229-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-07-04 16:17:40', '2014-07-05 02:17:40', '', '229', 'http://mauitropicalmassage.org/229-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
