ealing Table (alone, or with massage or energy work) </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>- Yoga</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>- Pilates, Gyrotonics &amp; other fitness lessons</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>- Waterfall hike &amp; cave meditation (serene spots that many Maui locals dont even know about!)</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>- Catered Gourmet Vegetarian/Vegan/Raw foods</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>* CHOOSE YOUR OWN HEALTH ADVENTURE ON MAGIC MAUI !!!</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n&nbsp;', '', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '26-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-18 23:04:31', '2014-09-19 09:04:31', '', '26', 'http://mauitropicalmassage.com/26-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
